## BP-005-T01: Forward tracing

test TC-T01-01 "Forward trace returns satisfying components"
  verifies: BP-005-T01
  given: a SystemModel where COMP-A satisfies REQ-001 and
         COMP-B does not
  when: the Tracer is queried forward with from_id REQ-001
  expect: the returned chain for REQ-001 has satisfied_by
          including "COMP-A" and not "COMP-B"

test TC-T01-02 "Forward trace returns verifying test specs"
  verifies: BP-005-T01
  given: a SystemModel where TC-001 verifies REQ-001
  when: the Tracer is queried forward with from_id REQ-001
  expect: the returned chain for REQ-001 has verified_by
          including "TC-001"

test TC-T01-03 "Allocated derived requirements count toward satisfying"
  verifies: BP-005-T01
  given: a derived requirement REQ-001-A with allocated_to COMP-X,
         and COMP-X does not list REQ-001-A in satisfies
  when: the Tracer is queried forward with from_id REQ-001-A
  expect: satisfied_by includes "COMP-X"

## BP-005-T02: Backward tracing

test TC-T02-01 "Backward from test spec returns verified requirements"
  verifies: BP-005-T02
  given: TC-001 verifies REQ-001 and REQ-002
  when: the Tracer is queried backward with from_id TC-001
  expect: the TraceResult contains chains for REQ-001 and REQ-002

test TC-T02-02 "Backward from component returns allocated requirements"
  verifies: BP-005-T02
  given: COMP-X satisfies REQ-001 and REQ-002-A is allocated_to COMP-X
  when: the Tracer is queried backward with from_id COMP-X
  expect: the TraceResult contains chains for REQ-001 and REQ-002-A

## BP-005-T03: Derived requirement chain

test TC-T03-01 "Ancestor chain walks derived_from links"
  verifies: BP-005-T03
  given: REQ-001 is system-level and REQ-001-A derives from REQ-001
  when: AncestorChain is called with REQ-001-A
  expect: the returned chain is ["REQ-001-A", "REQ-001"]

test TC-T03-02 "System-level requirement has a chain of length one"
  verifies: BP-005-T03
  given: REQ-001 is a system-level requirement with no derived_from
  when: AncestorChain is called with REQ-001
  expect: the returned chain is ["REQ-001"]

test TC-T03-03 "Broken derived_from stops the chain"
  verifies: BP-005-T03
  given: REQ-X has derived_from REQ-MISSING which does not exist
  when: AncestorChain is called with REQ-X
  expect: the returned chain stops at REQ-X and does not
          attempt to follow a missing link

## BP-005-T04: Full traceability matrix

test TC-T04-01 "Matrix contains a chain for every requirement"
  verifies: BP-005-T04
  given: a SystemModel with three requirements
  when: Matrix is called
  expect: the TraceResult contains three chains, one per
          requirement, in requirements-list order

test TC-T04-02 "Matrix chains include satisfied_by and verified_by"
  verifies: BP-005-T04
  given: REQ-001 is satisfied by COMP-A and verified by TC-001
  when: Matrix is called
  expect: the chain for REQ-001 has satisfied_by ["COMP-A"]
          and verified_by ["TC-001"]
